values:
Why? 
Really. 
Why? 

I barely made it back to my room, I stopped in the bathroom to take another shower. I tried to get the water really hot, but it wouldn't. Figures. I don't even know what to write, I'm not even sure if I want to write. I'm shaking and my head hurts from stopping myself from crying. I took medicine already, I had to stop myself from bringing out that bottle of vodka I told Aoi about so long ago. That'd be a perfect way to just relax.&nbsp; 

I feel really empty right now. Worn out. I feel like my muscles are melting along with everything else. I can't imagine what it'll be like when I wake up tomorrow morning with Escort knocking on my door.&nbsp; 

But the truth really is...I've never fallen this hard.
